excerpt.rendered:
EternalHealth’s Vitamin K2 (MK7) provides just the right formula of vitamin k complex to maximize the benefits of vitamin d.

Vitamin D3 ensures calcium absorption and Vitamin K2 directs the calcium to your bones and not to your vital organs, where it can be fatal.
